<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344000' id='t-344000'>It's easy to dismiss this as the perhaps well-intentioned</span>
