<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376000' id='t-376000'>But based on what data?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378000' id='t-378000'>Very little. Very little. Morphology and a lot of guesswork.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382000' id='t-382000'>Well, what I'm going to talk about today,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384000' id='t-384000'>what I'm going to talk about now is a new approach to this problem.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='387000' id='t-387000'>Instead of going out and guessing about our ancestry,</span>
