</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400000' id='t-400000'>what we need to do is turn the problem on its head.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402000' id='t-402000'>Because what we're really asking is a genealogical problem,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='406000' id='t-406000'>or a genealogical question.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408000' id='t-408000'>What we're trying to do is construct a family tree for everybody alive today.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>And as any genealogist will tell you --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='415000' id='t-415000'>anybody have a member of the family, or maybe you</span>
