</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449000' id='t-449000'>Who were these people who came before?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='451000' id='t-451000'>We have no written record. Well, actually, we do.</span>
