<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463000' id='t-463000'>Now, a quick primer on DNA.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465000' id='t-465000'>I suspect that not everybody in the audience is a geneticist.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468000' id='t-468000'>It is a very long, linear molecule, a coded version</span>
