<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475000' id='t-475000'>It's composed of four subunits: A, C, G and T, we call them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478000' id='t-478000'>And it's the sequence of those subunits that defines that blueprint.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482000' id='t-482000'>How long is it? Well, it's billions of these subunits in length.</span>
