<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='496000' id='t-496000'>If you take all the DNA out of one cell in your body,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='499000' id='t-499000'>and stretch it end to end, it's around two meters long.</span>
